data.description: ON GOLF COURSE!10' Ceilings and 8' doors. 3 bedrooms, den, 2.5 bath, 3 car garage. A wall of windows & sliding glass doors open to the large, covered patio, w/water feature, golf course & southern views. Family room features a gas fireplace & built-in entertainment center. Spacious kitchen has double ovens, an island, granite counters & backsplash, tile floors & plantation shutters. Large master w/bay window & views.  Master closet has organizers
